additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. Keep out of reach of children. Extremely flammable. Protect from sunlight and do not expose to temperatures exceeding 50C. Do not pierce or burn, even after use. Pressurised dispenser. Use only as directed. May burst if heated. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label and hand. Keep away from heat, hot surfaces, sparks, open flames and other ignition source. No smoking. Do not spray on an open flame or other ignition sources.
